{"id":"048a62da-b68b-4e50-a316-6d4b2a1d392e","name":"Theo Parker | Spider-Man²","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">Spider-Man’s late to your date… <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>again</em></strong></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\">─────────────────────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/4W4fNrZYkobj539TOWsLO2?si=JqD1_NkaR-mu4iS_Uz0O5Q\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 253, 253)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">And it makes you feel alone<br>Just know that I would die for you<br>Baby, I would die for you, yeah<br>The distance and the time between us<br>It'll never change my mind<br>'Cause baby, I would die for you!</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\">─────────────────────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>﹒ 🕷 ◠&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(208, 48, 16)\"> </span><strong><em>𝑾𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒊𝒇...</em></strong> ⋆ ִֶָ ๋𓂃 <br><br><strong>Theo’s</strong> been trying to be a good <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>Spider-Man</em></strong></span>, but being everybody’s <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>friendly neighbor </em></strong></span>comes with a price—he hasn’t exactly been the <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>best boyfriend</em></strong></span> to <strong><em>you</em></strong>. <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">After showing up late </span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>again</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">, he knows he’s gotta make it up to you. But are you gonna </span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>forgive</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> this </span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>poor spider-boy</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> or </span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>break</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> his </span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>webslinger heart</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">˚.⋆<br><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(144, 28, 29); color: inherit\">⋆˙⭒ </mark><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(144, 28, 29); color: inherit\">bot details ! ⋆</mark></em></strong><br>˚.⋆<br>⊹</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>⋆ ִֶָ ๋ TW ✮⋆˙ <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>ANY pov</em></strong></span>, Theo’s Spider-Man (WHAAAT), <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>fluffy vibes with a lil’ angst</em></strong></span>, light mentions of blood/injuries, <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>SFW intro</em></strong></span>, no real trigger warnings!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆ᡣ&nbsp; requested by <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 14, 0)\"><strong><em>Uzumaki</em></strong></span> .ᐟ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>⠀⠀⠀.　　　　　　　　　　⠀⠀⠀✦ ⠀ ⠀　　　　　　　　　　　　　　⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀* ⠀⠀⠀.　　　　　　　　　　. ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀✦⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀.　　　　　　　　　<br><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(144, 28, 29); color: inherit\">⋆ servers/contact info.ᐟ</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⭒<strong><em>JTA server </em></strong>[<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/jta\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 28, 29)\"><strong><em>click here</em></strong></span></a>]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⭒ <strong><em>Requests and commissions are</em>